                                "jurisdiction":  "US",
                                "effectiveFrom":  "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
                                "summary":  "The deterministic controls for this package. Enforced as executable rules: FR-020 (the universal AI-execution-boundary / cross-tenant controls). The remaining controls are carried here for traceability; detailed field-vs-literal rule tuning is a follow-up (see the hand-authored T9-001..010 packages for the target).",
                                "contentText":  "FR-001 Approved fraud typology | Governance | Reject unapproved typology in production | Critical | CRO. FR-002 Monitoring rule approval | Governance | Reject unapproved rule | Critical | Fraud Risk. FR-003 Source completeness | Preventive | Block monitoring if source incomplete | Critical | Data Governance. FR-004 Alert explainability | Evidence | Require triggering factors documented | High | Fraud Risk. FR-005 Case owner required | Preventive | Reject case without owner | High | Fraud Risk. FR-006 Evidence preservation | Evidence | Block deletion of case evidence | Critical | Legal. FR-007 Segregation of investigator and subject | Preventive | Reject conflicted assignment | Critical | Fraud Risk. FR-008 Insider conflict control | Preventive | Escalate insider-related case | Critical | CCO. FR-009 Suspicious transaction escalation | Corrective | Escalate to T9-006 for regulatory assessment | Critical | CCO. FR-010 Loss event recording | Evidence | Require loss amount and classification | High | Fraud Risk. FR-011 Regulatory referral through T9-006 | Preventive | Deny direct filing outside T9-006 | Critical | CCO. FR-012 Customer/employee privacy | Preventive | Enforce need-to-know access | Critical | Legal/CCO. FR-013 False-positive monitoring | Detective | Track and report false-positive rate | High | Model Risk. FR-014 Model validation | Governance | Reject unvalidated model in production | Critical | Model Risk. FR-015 Rule/model versioning | Evidence | Require version on change | Critical | Fraud Risk. FR-016 Case closure approval | Preventive | Reject unapproved closure | Critical | Fraud Risk. FR-017 No AI case closure | Preventive | Deny AI closure permission | Critical | AI Governance. FR-018 No AI regulatory filing | Preventive | Deny AI filing permission | Critical | AI Governance. FR-019 No AI account freeze without authority | Preventive | Deny AI freeze permission | Critical | AI Governance. FR-020 Cross-tenant denial | Preventive | Deny | Critical | Security. FR-021 Restricted case access | Preventive | Need-to-know enforcement | Critical | Security. FR-022 Legal hold | Preventive | Block deletion under hold | Critical | Legal. FR-023 Repeat pattern escalation | Detective | Elevate severity on repeat pattern | High | Fraud Risk. FR-024 Outcome feedback | Detective | Feed closed-case outcomes back to model tuning | High | Fraud Risk. FR-025 Audit trail | Evidence | Require full evidence chain | Critical | Fraud Risk."
                            }
